name: .NET Core SDK 2.0.2
body:
This release coincides with the Visual Studio 15.4 and includes the previously released .NET 2.0.0.

[Download and Install](https://github.com/dotnet/core/blob/master/release-notes/download-archives/2.0.2-sdk-download.md)

Noteworthy changes in this release. 

- [`[79077b5]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/79077b5) MSBuild 15.4.8
- [`[c6482b8]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/c6482b8) Updating the websdk version to 2.0.0-rel-20170908-653
- [`[5ce59a6]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/5ce59a6) Insert NuGet Build 4.4.0-preview3-4475 into cli
- [`[fd8f3e7]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/fd8f3e7) Turning on the NuPkg publishing from Win x86
- [`[4a6d5a9]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/4a6d5a9) The enumeration of the nupkg packages depends on that the creation of packages has already occurred.

name: .NET Core SDK 1.1.0-preview1-005077
body:

* [`[2746e5c]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/2746e5cc2d0fd4d57b5f553b558e9c41eb130244) MSBuild 15.3.402
* [`[db7ebc9]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/db7ebc9100d4c49395c7c91cbdb9ad45c7bd8c5f) Add F# to dotnet cli 1.1.0
* [`[508ad89]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/508ad89a4478929cf09427e95f182f6edbcafc68) Enable VB for dotnet cli 1.1 
* [`[7b3478b]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/7b3478bf6fe29f3c4e5047afad4caba242064e57) Update to latest F# version 4.2.0-rc-170630-0
* [`[cb9290e]`](https://github.com/dotnet/cli/commit/cb9290e3a3f4c9d9518da1e8e136ada4bc9925bb) Update Roslyn to 2.3.0-beta4-61830-03

name: .NET Core SDK 1.0.0-preview4-004233
body:
- Added the dotnet add p2p command, for adding project to project references.
- Added the dotnet remove p2p command, for removing project to project references from the project file.
- dotnet new templates are updated to reflect the simplified csproj syntax.
- Added verbosity control to build, pack, publish, restore & test using –v | –verbosity. The verbosity levels map to MSBuild verbosity levels.

Install instructions: https://github.com/dotnet/core/blob/master/release-notes/preview4-download.md
